{"tid":366384,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣間唯一雲貴川真係變哂質","createTime":"2017-08-20T03:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T06:58:44.000Z","uid":20989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67c86c2f79e3ba1e6ee9196f7523283263bc9ba2","tid":366384,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:51:49.000Z","msg":"由好細個記憶模糊就成日食老母買既外賣<br />\n食到依家大學都就畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前我成日笑尻朋友去譚仔食餿水就係因為有呢間咁好食既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前幾日再去買 多油到仆街 麵又少左 腩肉唔再軟身<br />\n仲成日咬到d好硬既黑色唔知咩野 要吐返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f102dcb9a5c8712a5b3e23e4571a0fe5c07c834b","tid":366384,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:53:13.000Z","msg":"出左名99%HEA"},{"pid":"598c0f1f7d45bc936c4c3be92bced0c68dfb0458","tid":366384,"uid":33420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:55:13.000Z","msg":"石蔭雲南都差左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267b50d19aa3cefdc04c16ffb6df90157875e346","tid":366384,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T04:10:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出左名99%HEA</blockquote><br />\n之前唔知邊度睇到話換過老細<br />\n但至少我認得某幾個阿姐係由細做到大"},{"pid":"76e2a0c6b6d69e7aeb182ae9d20af09ce8f9b533","tid":366384,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>石蔭雲南都差左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舖面太細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重點係啲餸紙咁薄"},{"pid":"03716980b39b23001b09521f080967791fbd4985","tid":366384,"uid":47798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由好細個記憶模糊就成日食老母買既外賣<br />\n食到依家大學都就畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前我成日笑尻朋友去譚仔食餿水就係因為有呢間咁好食既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前幾日再去買 多油到仆街 麵又少左 腩肉唔再軟身<br />\n仲成日咬到d好硬既黑色唔知咩野 要吐返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自從有次食到佢個匙羹有漂白水味之後就無再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申由細食到大腩肉蘿蔔多蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871ee6a636f40eaa96c60e7c83b3ebb8a9f548a8","tid":366384,"uid":69275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T23:51:01.000Z","msg":"基本上出左名，質素難免下降"},{"pid":"98a94611c64daa728db94f08e17f7f53c3bac4af","tid":366384,"uid":56775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:41:33.000Z","msg":"細個睇雜誌個老閭係紅磡鋪果個 早一兩係紅磡食過一次老闆話荃灣店唔再關事 好似係頂左手俾親戚"},{"pid":"5b48363d0f147af743f75e2458d545cd7ba27c64","tid":366384,"uid":11285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:45:24.000Z","msg":"面頭成層油<br />\nd米線就水汪汪無味嘅<br />\n係港豬先會排黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd27b02f632d3cb2bcb2084906aac9410247da0e","tid":366384,"uid":128805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T00:46:42.000Z","msg":"太多人排隊，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d1c3d5a98faf4aa8ed73113283526dc20a817a","tid":366384,"uid":139345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"每次同朋友出街都會同佢食呢間，佢好中意食...<br />\n老實講，40幾蚊一碗米線又唔係特別好食，唔知點解每次都排咁多人，如果唔係同朋友一齊都唔食<br />\n<br />\n比多10幾蚊食三哥過期米線仲好食過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582889015e6d554c2f8912274d04153956639146","tid":366384,"uid":58699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>石蔭雲南都差左 <img sr